Healing Performance		KEY:Healing Performance ~ Songhealer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.BardicPerformance																																																																							DESC:You can use your performance to create an effect equivalent to heal on a living target (or harm on an undead target), using your level as the caster level. Using this ability requires 5 rounds of continuous performance, and the target must be able to see and hear the bard throughout the performance. The healing performance relies on audible and visual components.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.27
