Dragon Bite			KEY:Dragon Bite ~ Dragon Shaman		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArchetypeDruid.SpecialAttack.Supernatural				DESC:Your bite attack (whether using totem transformation or wild shape to take the form of a lizard) deals +1d6 points of energy damage (acid, cold, electricity, or fire). You choose what kind of energy damage that you deal each time you bite.	SOURCEPAGE:p.38
