###Block: Storm Druid
Spontaneous Domain Casting	KEY:Spontaneous Domain Casting ~ Storm Druid		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArchetypeDruid.SpecialQuality				DESC:You can channel stored spell energy into domain spells that you have not prepared ahead of time. You can "lose" a prepared spell in order to cast any domain spell of the same level or lower.	SOURCEPAGE:p.40
Nature Bond			KEY:Nature's Bond ~ Storm Druid				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArchetypeDruid.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:You may not choose an animal companion. You must choose the Air or Weather domain, or the Cloud, Storm, or Wind subdomain.	SOURCEPAGE:p.40	DEFINE:DruidCloudAllowed|1	DEFINE:DruidStormsAllowed|1	DEFINE:DruidWindAllowed|1	DEFINE:DruidEarthNotAllowed|1	DEFINE:DruidFireNotAllowed|1	DEFINE:DruidWaterNotAllowed|1	DEFINE:DruidAnimalNotAllowed|1	DEFINE:DruidPlantNotAllowed|1	DEFINE:DruidAnimalTerrainDomainNotAllowed|1	DEFINE:AnimalCompanionNotAllowed|1
Windwalker				KEY:Windwalker ~ Storm Druid					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArchetypeDruid.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:The penalties from natural or magical wind effects (see page 439 of the Core Rulebook) are treated as one step less severe for you.	SOURCEPAGE:p.40
Stormvoice				KEY:Stormvoice ~ Storm Druid					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArchetypeDruid.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:Your voice can magically carry over howling winds and peals of thunder. Whenever a Perception check is needed to hear your voice, the DC is reduced by %1.|StormVoiceReduction	DEFINE:StormVoiceReduction|classlevel("Druid")	SOURCEPAGE:p.40
Eyes of the Storm			KEY:Eyes of the Storm ~ Storm Druid				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArchetypeDruid.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:You can see through %1 feet of magical fog, mist, gas, wind, rain, or similar inclement weather conditions, ignoring any concealment it might grant.|EyesOfTheStormRange	DEFINE:EyesOfTheStormRange|5*(floor(classlevel("Druid")/4)+1)	SOURCEPAGE:p.40
Windlord				KEY:Windlord ~ Storm Druid					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArchetypeDruid.SpecialQuality				DESC:You can select another domain or subdomain from those available to you through your nature bond.	SOURCEPAGE:p.40	BONUS:DOMAIN|NUMBER|1	BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Druid Domain|1
Storm Lord				KEY:Storm Lord ~ Storm Druid					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArchetypeDruid.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:You are unaffected by natural and magical wind effects. You also become immune to deafness and gain +2 bonus on saving throws against sonic effects.	SOURCEPAGE:p.40	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Immunity to Deafness

